book-forge is inspired by the *methodology* described in autonovel's
documentation, including:
  - The 5-layer + canon-truth-DB model of a book.
  - The modify-evaluate-keep/discard loop wrapped around quality checks.
  - The use of multiple "immune systems" (mechanical, judge, panel)
